{"tid":2201942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蠱惑兩地牌車改裝設暗格 藏40公斤 乾鮑入珠","createTime":"2020-09-14T07:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T08:28:03.000Z","uid":51724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4eccbd46f78a3da7fc3f40f0bad2b3d3180350f","tid":2201942,"uid":51724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"拱北海關昨（11）日在港珠澳大橋口岸，揭發一架粵澳兩地牌私家車企圖透過車內暗格走私40公斤乾鮑到內地。<br />\n拱北海關稱，關員在入境客車通道查驗涉事私家車時發現異常，車主承認曾經改裝車輛，並設有 3個暗格，關員之後在暗格內發現這批乾鮑，估計約值20萬元人民幣。案件已移交緝私部門作進一步處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.exmoo.com/article/157707.html?fbclid=IwAR0pgZWw6trvZ0m-MYssHWo3QGcYjbcvG2305XJ-sHnKHxGVbDxXOKLK1ZI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.exmoo.com%2Farticle%2F157707.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0pgZWw6trvZ0m-MYssHWo3QGcYjbcvG2305XJ-sHnKHxGVbDxXOKLK1ZI&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8Bdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=3c20fad1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.exmoo.com/article/157707.html?fbclid=IwAR0pgZWw6trvZ0m-MYssHWo3QGcYjbcvG2305XJ-sHnKHxGVbDxXOKLK1ZI</a>"},{"pid":"0f8d7e5b84bbbdf92ca56fd420b9e99229e6f146","tid":2201942,"uid":224533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"官員fat fat有免費鮑魚食仲有罰款收<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f76f2c5ff933177c2c992c72353281b17bcb07","tid":2201942,"uid":13450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"依d新聞黎架咩<br />\n30年前已經係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}